{"name": "Collective Focus Resource Hub", "alternate_name": "", "description": "- We recommend community members arrive at 12pm to collect a ticket and make the line. 
- They  also have community fridges outside at 1046 Broadway Bedford-Stuyvesant, NY 11221 that they stock from food rescues three times a week.
- Sunday, Monday, Wednesday food fridge rescues are in the evening depending on dropoff time
- Closed for thanksgiving holiday
